    "description": "Capital is an open world, destruction focused, non-linear, first and third person action-adventure shooter, inspired by games like GTA Max Payne and Red Faction. Freely explore the entire island, buy or steal items from shops, purchase houses to store more vehicles and have a better fortress to defend when taking refuge from law enforcement.  All buildings are destructible, break into secured rooms and destroy safes for higher value loot.  Buy and upgrade cars.  Customize clothing. Become a true capitalist and decimate the enemy with superior fire power.<br><br>Enter every building, steal low value items off of the shelves or blast your way to the good stuff!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/df06216d130ea19ace7779b3867e0980.poster.avif?t=1766272171\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/df06216d130ea19ace7779b3867e0980.webm?t=1766272171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/df06216d130ea19ace7779b3867e0980.mp4?t=1766272171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Purchase or steal heavy equipment for the highest value targets<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/fd5e3c81f59f37cc81af3bcf8476817b.poster.avif?t=1766272171\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/fd5e3c81f59f37cc81af3bcf8476817b.webm?t=1766272171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/fd5e3c81f59f37cc81af3bcf8476817b.mp4?t=1766272171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Leave the enemy guessing by destroying their infrastructure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/aaaa462d1e4a3c15218d5cf401bb987f.poster.avif?t=1766272171\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/aaaa462d1e4a3c15218d5cf401bb987f.webm?t=1766272171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059150/extras/aaaa462d1e4a3c15218d5cf401bb987f.mp4?t=1766272171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features Include:<br><br>Usable cars, tanks, and helicopters<br>Vehicular Combat<br>Car trunk storage<br>Medical Enhancement<br>Inventory system with quick slots and customizable clothing<br>Merchant systems<br>Ability to purchase new safehouses with more car storage<br>Destructible everything (except ground and foliage)<br>Enemy substations that can be destroyed strategically<br>A 6 level police system with an attack helicopter at level 6<br>NPC civilians<br>Traffic<br>Fire system<br>Slow motion<br>Player mappable controls<br>Quick save currently only one slot (MAY have to reset saves on some updates)<br>Scalability options",
